ygData.msgSnippet: I beg to differ.  I made level 12-13-14-15 in Unrest soloing Jacks, Tormenteds, Death Beetles, and the occasional ghoul.  Just stay close to the wall and NEVER
ygData.messageBody:
I beg to differ. I made level 12-13-14-15 in Unrest soloing Jacks,
Tormenteds, Death Beetles, and the occasional ghoul. Just stay close to the
wall and NEVER pull an undead across the path of the death beetles or you
will have a group on you that will shred you very fast.
